window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Dragons with assault cannons? How is that fair?</p> <p>I saved Highspire and the academy from the dissolution of our world. Seventeen-thousand students survived, and I want to keep it that way. The ship is breaking down. Life support needs repairs, and we have almost no food. We need money badly. That means scavenging tech that we can sell to the same people who blew up our planet.</p> <p>Fortunately I'm the best Relic Hunter in the business...though to be fair all the rest died when my world tumbled into the sun.</p> <p>There are six other Great Ships out there, and who knows what we'll find inside? I'm sure it will be fine. What could possibly go wrong?</p>"; 
